exert force to the tumor cells. There's a compression force.

13
00:00:45.420 --> 00:00:47.600
There are also topological differences.

14
00:00:48.140 --> 00:00:52.100
And when the tumor cells get out of the circulation and get into

15
00:00:52.140 --> 00:00:54.280
the circulation, there's also shear force.

16
00:00:54.760 --> 00:00:58.520
So during this very complex journey, when the primary

17
00:00:58.600 --> 00:01:02.000
tumor form and then become metastatic and arrive in a

18
00:01:02.080 --> 00:01:05.710
different organ, there's variety of physical forces

19
00:01:06.160 --> 00:01:09.940
that actually, I think we will present data to

20
